Use DNS over https with cURL curl --doh-url https://dns.google/dns-query https://api.ipify.org Note The above command will override the DNS server while quering api.ipify.org, but it will still use your system DNS to query for dns.google
You can view list of DNS servers here.
Use curl to telnet to another machine curl telnet://&lt;ip address or hostname&gt;:&lt;port&gt;
